karina niki jett (n√©e mikelis) is a professional poker player. she may be best known for her appearances on the gsn series poker royale battle of the sexes. jett also appeared in late night poker's fourth season. her husband is fellow full tilt poker pro chip jett, one of the world's foremost tournament players. the couple writes a column together for card player magazine, answering reader questions in a "he said/she said" format. at the 2011 wsop, jett finished second in the ladies championship. this was the third time she made the final table in this event. as of 2014, her total live tournament winnings exceed $500,000.